          The gates of Heaven are closed shut; the realm of Hell  consumed by
          flood. And in their wake, countless parallel  worlds  wither  away,
          one after the other. The surviving angels and demons gather  at the
          city  they  believe to  be their  final chance  at  salvation:  the
          floating purgatory of "Tokyo Babel". Joined by humans,  they embark
          on a pilgrimage across the seven layers of Babel, hoping  to ascend
          Jacob's Ladder in an effort to re-open the gates of Heaven.
